@gateway_url = http://localhost:5000

### ========== GATEWAY INFO ==========

### Gateway Info
GET {{gateway_url}}/

### Gateway Health Check
GET {{gateway_url}}/health

### ========== EHR SERVICE (via Gateway) ==========

### Tạo EHR mới
POST {{gateway_url}}/api/ehr/records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "createdByDoctorId": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222",
  "encounterId": "33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333",
  "hospitalId": "44444444-4444-4444-4444-444444444444",
  "reportType": "LAB",
  "data": {
    "testName": "Complete Blood Count",
    "results": {
      "wbc": 7500,
      "rbc": 4.8,
      "hemoglobin": 14.2
    }
  }
}

### Lấy EHR theo ID (thay {ehrId} bằng ID thực)
@ehrId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
GET {{gateway_url}}/api/ehr/records/{{ehrId}}

### Lấy EHR theo Patient ID
@patientId = 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
GET {{gateway_url}}/api/ehr/records/patient/{{patientId}}

### Lấy EHR versions
GET {{gateway_url}}/api/ehr/records/{{ehrId}}/versions

### Lấy EHR files
GET {{gateway_url}}/api/ehr/records/{{ehrId}}/files

### ========== AUTH SERVICE (via Gateway) ==========

### Auth Health Check
GET {{gateway_url}}/api/auth/health
